title: United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Salt Sulphur Earths & Sto
description: Imports of Intra EU - Salt, Sulphur, Earths & Sto in the United Kingdom decreased to 64.87 GBP Million in September from 77.99 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Intra EU - Salt, Sulphur, Earths & Sto in the United Kingdom averaged 29 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 77.99 GBP Million in August of 2022 and a record low of 10.87 GBP Million in May of 1996. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Salt, Sulphur, Earths & Sto.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
